body:
@benoitsteiner 
I changed `channels` as per your request;  sadly, there is a distinction for the others. 
`rows_out`, `rows_in`, and etc are actually used as scalar underneath, where they do scalar-ish things like serving as for-loop constraints, getting passed into `range`, and etc.  So, a significant rewrite would be required if I wanted to let `rows_in` to be a tensor.
